fr</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="220" x="63.5" y="200.373">: &#35745;&#31639;&#24739;&#32773;PICO&#19982;&#35777;&#25454;PICO&#30340;&#30456;&#20284;&#24230;&#24471;&#20998;</text><rect fill="#CCE5FF" height="33.9688" rx="12.5" ry="12.5" style="stroke:#007BFF;stroke-width:1.0;" width="222" x="57" y="233.2031"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" font-weight="bold" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="14" x="67" y="254.3418">fh</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="188" x="81" y="254.3418">: &#26597;&#34920;&#33719;&#21462;&#35777;&#25454;&#36136;&#37327;&#31561;&#32423;&#23545;&#24212;&#30340;&#25968;&#20540;</text><rect fill="#CCE5FF" height="33.9688" rx="12.5" ry="12.5" style="stroke:#007BFF;stroke-width:1.0;" width="221" x="57.5" y="287.1719"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" font-weight="bold" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="13" x="67.5" y="308.3105">fs</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="188" x="80.5" y="308.3105">: &#26597;&#34920;&#33719;&#21462;&#25512;&#33616;&#24378;&#24230;&#31561;&#32423;&#23545;&#24212;&#30340;&#25968;&#20540;</text><rect fill="#CCE5FF" height="33.9688" rx="12.5" ry="12.5" style="stroke:#007BFF;stroke-width:1.0;" width="158" x="89" y="341.1406"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="24" x="99" y="362.2793">&#35745;&#31639;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" font-weight="bold" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="110" x="127" y="362.2793">BEV = fr * fh * fs</text><rect fill="#FFFFFF" height="340.0469" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1.0;" width="324" x="6" y="397.1094"/><path d="M195,397.1094 L195,406.4063 L185,416.4063 L6,416.4063 " fill="none" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1.0;"/><text fill="#000000" font-famil