" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="24" x="56.5" y="858.5605">&#35745;&#31639;</text><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" font-weight="bold" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="195" x="84.5" y="858.5605">Final_Score = BEV * (1 + CM)</text><rect fill="#CCE5FF" height="33.9688" rx="12.5" ry="12.5" style="stroke:#007BFF;stroke-width:1.0;" width="223" x="56.5" y="903.3906"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="203" x="66.5" y="924.5293">&#23558;&#35745;&#31639;&#20986;&#30340;Final_Score&#36171;&#32473;&#35813;&#35777;&#25454;&#39033;</text><rect fill="#CCE5FF" height="33.9688" rx="12.5" ry="12.5" style="stroke:#007BFF;stroke-width:1.0;" width="223" x="56.5" y="957.3594"/><text fill="#000000" font-family="Verdana" font-size="12" lengthAdjust="spacing" textLength="203" x="66.5" y="978.498">&#23545;&#25152;&#26377;&#35777;&#25454;&#39033;&#25353;Final_Score&#38477;&#24207;&#25490;&#24207;</text><ellipse cx="168" cy="1022.3281" fill="none" rx="11" ry="11" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1.0;"/><ellipse cx="168" cy="1022.3281" fill="#FFFFFF" rx="6" ry="6" style="stroke:#000000;stroke-width:1.0;"/><line style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;" x1="168" x2="168" y1="25" y2="45"/><polygon fill="#333333" points="164,35,168,45,172,35,168,39" style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;"/><line style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;" x1="168" x2="168" y1="159.2344" y2="179.2344"/><polygon fill="#333333" points="164,169.2344,168,179.2344,172,169.2344,168,173.2344" style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;"/><line style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;" x1="168" x2="168" y1="213.2031" y2="233.2031"/><polygon fill="#333333" points="164,223.2031,168,233.2031,172,223.2031,168,227.2031" style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;"/><line style="stroke:#333333;stroke-width:1.0;" x1="168" x2="168" y1="267.1719" y2="287.1719"/><polygon fill="#333333" points="164,277.1719,168,287.1719,172,277.1719,168,281